value: They agree to meet at the fountain.\nBut it appears only one shows up...
It's like they're on parallel paths.\nHow long until they find each other?
The water stops and they lock eyes!\nThey blush with embarrassment.
The fountain mesmerizes them both...\nA lovely sight thanks to the confusion.
Forma units cannot be used as source Heroes\nfor skill inheritance, including Rearmed Heroes.
